lt=\".\" style=\"background-color: inherit\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><img src=\"tbl_vjoin_end.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: inherit\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><img src=\"icon-q-coding.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: white; background-color: inherit\" title=\"coding\" class=\"hierarchy\"/> data-delivery.archive</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">Data Archive System</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">0..1</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-item-type.html#item-type-choice\">choice</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">Options: <a href=\"#opt-item.data-delivery.archive\">1 option</a><br/>Initial Value: Coding = <a href=\"CodeSystem-nasa-data-archive-cs.html\" title=\"https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data-archive-cs\">NASA Medical Data Archive Systems</a>#areas \"Astronaut Radiation Exposure Assessment System\"</td></tr>#xD;\n<tr><td colspan=\"6\" class=\"hierarchy\"><br/><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/formats.html#table\" title=\"Legend for this format\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"doco\" style=\"background-color: inherit\"/> Documentation for this format</a></td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Options Sets</b></p><a name=\"opt-item.overview.sponsor\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for overview.sponsor </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-mrid-sponsor-cs#srag (\"Space Radiation Analysis Group\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.overview.discipline\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for overview.discipline </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-mrid-discipline-cs#radiation (\"Radiation Health\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.contingency-event.type\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for contingency-event.type </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Equipment malfunction - elevated readings</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Shielding breach/damage</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Unexpected exposure during EVA</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Dosimeter alarm</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Radioactive source incident</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Other</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.exposure-assessment.dose-type\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for exposure-assessment.dose-type </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Whole body</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Skin/extremity</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Eye lens</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Mixed/uncertain</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.medical-assessment.symptoms\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for medical-assessment.symptoms </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Nausea</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Fatigue</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Skin erythema</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Headache</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Other</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.data-delivery.archive\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for data-delivery.archive </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data-archive-cs#areas (\"Astronaut Radiation Exposure Assessment System\")</li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
